Deserves every word of praise. Just perfect with seafood, fish or chicken. Without question, my favorite risotto. I've made it several times...including once when I added nickel sized pieces of ginger (easy to fish out at the end) to the oil at the beginning. It gives an additional layer of complexity that worked well for me.

