I thought this was a keeper! Don't do what I did, however, which was to add more lemon juice!! The amount in the recipe seemed light, so I added more--what a mistake! Also, I added asparagas cut into 1" pieces to the broth to cook. Then, about halfway through the risotto process, I added all the asparagas into the rice. The blend of lemon and asparagas was awesome!

